    "description": "<strong>God s' Margarita</strong> is a story-driven adventure and a walking simulation. The game takes place in the post-apocalyptic landscapes of AI Legave a thousand years into the future. After hiding from the world for two years, Reniat Noc travels through the vast environments of his homeland to reunite with his friend Elbep. On the road ahead, he will partake in many adventures, challenging situations, and discover the history of his abandoned homeland.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/cce5c2571e6c5e537b9d44f9975777a3.poster.avif?t=1712942418\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/cce5c2571e6c5e537b9d44f9975777a3.webm?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/cce5c2571e6c5e537b9d44f9975777a3.mp4?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>~&gt;</strong> UNCOVER YOUR FUTURE THROUGH THE PAST<br>Traverse the semi-open world, the wasteland of AI Legave to discover the history that will shape your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/307245a14bbff87ae6b434e5de0b4c04.poster.avif?t=1712942418\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/307245a14bbff87ae6b434e5de0b4c04.webm?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/307245a14bbff87ae6b434e5de0b4c04.mp4?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>~&gt;</strong> EMPLOY FUTURISTIC GADGETS AND ASSETS <br>Have you ever wished to walk on water? Well, now you can't... But! You can turn invisible, run with superhuman speed, and pass-through walls. Yep, that's the future all right!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/984e44354934b8a1679e801284f55ec3.poster.avif?t=1712942418\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/984e44354934b8a1679e801284f55ec3.webm?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/984e44354934b8a1679e801284f55ec3.mp4?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>~&gt;</strong> EXPLORE UNIQUE LOCATIONS<br>A thousand years in the future there will be everything left to explore! Especially when all the explorers are gone.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/5d45fa4f8a7077e0d48673dd8c2db762.poster.avif?t=1712942418\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/5d45fa4f8a7077e0d48673dd8c2db762.webm?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/5d45fa4f8a7077e0d48673dd8c2db762.mp4?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>~&gt;</strong> RELISH THE MIRACLES OF EXISTING ALONE<br>The hunting dreams, the unjudged imagination, the sound of the wind passing you by, the need to find your lost friend, the joy of running alone towards the unknown!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/8c3ab10eab4c21f364d4bc42f07668c4.poster.avif?t=1712942418\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/8c3ab10eab4c21f364d4bc42f07668c4.webm?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/8c3ab10eab4c21f364d4bc42f07668c4.mp4?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>~&gt;</strong> HOOK ALIEN FISH AND MORE<br>You will never know what is hidden inside the white muds. But you can fish it out!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/3c8690793fc593e8e1260d196b5c54a3.poster.avif?t=1712942418\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/3c8690793fc593e8e1260d196b5c54a3.webm?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898020/extras/3c8690793fc593e8e1260d196b5c54a3.mp4?t=1712942418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>~&gt;</strong> LOOK AT THE HORIZON AND UNDER THE ROCKS<br>Run, Discover, Collect, Face danger and challenges, Enjoy the loneliness, and embody the disposition of Reniat Noc.",
